* #1 NTA | Must Enter::HTHB | LTLB* 5 min Trend Side or Reversal + Price Bynd VWAP SD1 | 20 EMA 5 min Slanting  | 15min ORB
* High return if Entry is before important TL | RS Break / Reversal Violent move 
* Consol:: >2x 10 Co 20 EMA | Oscillate 20 EMA 5 min | within VWAP SD1 | 15 min OR
* Re-Entry::20, 50, 200 EMAs | VWAP | SPB 1x Swing E::Prices cont. Trend with 61% retrace Swing H/L + L/XL Candle | CPB 3x Swing E::Swing Trend L. Break | RSI 60/40 | Avoid > 3xSw
* All Intraday SL must, but Not big (SL hunt)
* Always Close Position using Trail SL ::70% of Peak profit | Prev Swing H/L | Prev Candle - H/L | 61% of L / XL | VWAP | 
* When price near | revers  important TL / RS (violent move expected) keep Tight Option SL using Option chart price. All other time keep arbitrary Option SL based on Spot LTLB | HTHB 5 min chart. 
* Never take position based on R/S or Elliot Wave alone. Point #1 must concur
* R/S & Profit Book:: T.Line, Recent Swing | Pre Day H/L, 10 min OR, CPR, HT EMA 1hr
* ORB T::10 min @ 9:25 | Trend T:: After 11 am 20 EMA x 5min
* On a Strong Trending week, Expiry may be on Trend Side Max, PB are Re-Entries
* Expiry -2 ~ -3 days Over Night Position (Max 20% Cap) as Risk vs Return is Good
* Expiry Trade::Max loss Day,  Avoid Over night position as Unfav Open loss induce Neg. mind set to Scaled & Over trade to cover Loss Over Trade  and Trade without Analysis.  Premium will Fall Fast during Open, Consolidation, Better Trade after 1:00pm with 50% SL and Max loss Limit. 
* Price movement before 2hrs before expiry is mystery. Beware of Reduced Premium induce Scaled Position, High leverage High loss & Overtrade too.
* On a strong trend any major RS bound to break, hence never close position near RS instead hold for violent price break of RS
* Can use Option Prices for re-entry and trail stop-loss